Feature: Product Service Administration
    As a Product Manager
    I want to manage the product inventory
    So that I can keep track of what we sell

Background:
    Given the following products
        | name       | description | price | available | category |
        | Fedora     | A hat       | 20    | True      | CLOTHS   |
        | Laptop     | A computer  | 500   | True      | ELECTRONICS |
        | iPhone     | A phone     | 800   | False     | ELECTRONICS |

Scenario: Reading a Product
    When I visit the "Home Page"
    And I set the "Name" to "Fedora"
    And I press the "Search" button
    Then I should see the message "Success"
    When I press the "Edit" button
    Then I should see "Fedora" in the "Name" field

Scenario: Updating a Product
    When I visit the "Home Page"
    And I set the "Name" to "Fedora"
    And I press the "Search" button
    Then I should see "Fedora" in the "Name" field
    When I set the "Name" to "New Fedora"
    And I press the "Update" button
    Then I should see the message "Success"
    When I press the "Clear" button
    And I set the "Name" to "New Fedora"
    And I press the "Search" button
    Then I should see "New Fedora" in the "Name" field
